BadGun - Class in Unnamed Package
The BadGun class is a subclass of the Weapon class, it represents a weaker weapon that is used by the student character.

This constructor is used to construct a new BadGun with the given name and power.
boost() - Method in class SuperGun
This method is used to set the value of Boosted to be true, which means that the SuperGun is now boosted and should have double the power until the round ends.
Boosted - Variable in class SuperGun
Boolean variable used to indicate whether the SuperGun is boosted
boostWeapon(SuperGun) - Method in class SecurityGuard
This method is used to boost the SuperGun weapon held by the security guard It calls the boost method of the SuperGun w1 This sets the Boosted instance variable of the SuperGun w1 to be true, and the SuperGun is now boosted.
